ww.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/12\/30\/ibn-abbas-remember-your-faults\/","url_meta":{"origin":35117,"position":3},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Humility: Remember your own faults before other people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 30, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Mujahid reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf you intend to mention the faults of your companions, then remember your own faults.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 328 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Bukhari Ibn Qudamah said, \"Beware of being preoccupied with rectifying others before you rectify\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25273,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/10\/11\/hudud-pardon-faults-not-crimes\/","url_meta":{"origin":35117,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hudud: Pardon good people their faults, not crimes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cOverlook the faults of good people, except for legal punishments.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4375 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u0647\u064e\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u